---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../index.scss";
---

<Layout
  title="My portfolio"
  description="Portfolio presents my current programming skills, knowledge and stack"
>
  <main class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
    <section class="hero container">
      <div class="hero__content">
        <h1 class="hero--title">Travel without limits!</h1>
        <p class="hero--description">
          Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consecte tur adipisicing elit. Soluta ut
          facere aliquam impedit ullam minusreprehenderit quia in laudantium
          sint.
        </p>
        <button class="hero--cta">Check offer</button>
      </div>
      <div id="modal" class="modal-wrapper">
        <div class="modal-container">
          <div class="modal-header">
            <button class="modal-icon--close">
              <img src=" /astro-lp/cross.svg" alt="cross icon" />
              <span class="sr-only">Cross icon to close modal</span>
            </button>
            <h2 class="modal--title">Modal title</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-content">
            <p class="modal--description">
              Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Tempore
              ea consequuntur cupiditate sequi. Ipsa iste dignissimos, odit
              natus nisi quod ipsam dolorum quae temporibus similique expedita
              error ad quo corporis ipsum ea cumque provident, accusantium quia
              perspiciatis? Id pariatur eligendi ex nisi quos magnam non ipsum
              odit beatae! Sint, voluptatum?
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="modal-footer">
            <button class="modal-btn modal-btn--close">close</button>
            <button class="modal-btn modal-btn--confirm">confirm</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section
      class="projects w-full max-h-none flex flex-col items-center p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-300 to-blue-200"
    >
      <div class="max-w-6xl">
        <h2 class="title mb-12 text-4xl font-semibold">
          Portfolio Highlights: Showcasing My Work
        </h2>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base">
          Welcome to my Portfolio Highlights section, where I present a curated
          selection of my finest work. Here, you'll find a collection of
          projects that showcase my skills, creativity, and expertise. From
          innovative designs to successful campaigns, each project reflects my
          dedication to delivering high-quality results and exceeding
          expectations.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-6 text-base">
          Explore this gallery to gain insight into my capabilities and see how
          I can bring value to your projects. Whether you're seeking design
          inspiration, marketing strategies, or technical solutions, my
          portfolio highlights demonstrate my ability to tackle diverse
          challenges and deliver outstanding outcomes. Dive in and discover the
          depth of my professional experience and the breadth of my creative
          vision.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-24">
          <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-16">
            <li class="flex justify-stretch">
              <div class="p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-x-6 shadow-md">
                <div class="h-64">
                  <img
                    class="rounded-3xl w-64 h-64"
                    src="astro-lp/project_1.png"
                    alt="Location-based weather API"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="relative h-full pb-8">
                  <h3
                    class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-7 tracking-tight text-gray-900"
                  >
                    Weather App
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-700 my-8"
                  >
                    Stay ahead of the forecast with our intuitive weather app.
                    Get real-time updates on current conditions, hourly
                    forecasts, and daily outlooks. Plan your day confidently
                    with accurate weather information at your fingertips. Never
                    be caught off guard by the elements again!
                  </p>
                  <p class="w-full flex justify-around absolute bottom-0">
                    <span class="text-orange-600">HTML</span>
                    <span class="text-blue-600">CSS</span>
                    <span class="text-yellow-300">JavaScript</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li class="flex justify-stretch">
              <div class="p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-x-6 shadow-md">
                <div class="h-64">
                  <img
                    class="w-64 h-64 rounded-3xl"
                    src="astro-lp/project_2.png"
                    alt="Location-based weather API"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="relative h-full pb-8">
                  <h3
                    class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-7 tracking-tight text-gray-900"
                  >
                    Age calculator
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-700 my-8"
                  >
                    AgeEase: Instantly calculate your age or anyone else's with
                    precision and simplicity. Whether you're celebrating
                    milestones or planning events, keeps track of the years,
                    months, and days. Effortlessly determine ages for birthdays,
                    anniversaries, or any special occasion.
                  </p>
                  <p class="w-full flex justify-around absolute bottom-0">
                    <span class="text-orange-600">HTML</span>
                    <span class="text-blue-600">CSS</span>
                    <span class="text-yellow-300">JavaScript</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-stretch">
              <div class="p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-x-6 shadow-md">
                <div class="h-64">
                  <img
                    class="w-64 h-64 rounded-3xl"
                    src="astro-lp/project_3.png"
                    alt="Location-based weather API"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="relative h-full pb-8">
                  <h3
                    class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-7 tracking-tight text-gray-900"
                  >
                    Real Estate
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-700 my-8"
                  >
                    Introducing Real Estate: Your trusted partner in real estate
                    management. From residential complexes to commercial spaces,
                    we offer comprehensive property management services tailored
                    to meet your needs. With a focus on efficiency,
                    transparency, and maximizing property value.
                  </p>
                  <p class="w-full flex justify-around absolute bottom-0">
                    <span class="text-orange-600">HTML</span>
                    <span class="text-blue-600">CSS</span>
                    <span class="text-yellow-300">JavaScript</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex justify-stretch">
              <div class="p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-x-6 shadow-md">
                <div class="h-64">
                  <img
                    class="w-64 h-64 rounded-3xl"
                    src="astro-lp/project_4.png"
                    alt="Location-based weather API"
                  />
                </div>
                <div class="relative h-full pb-8">
                  <h3
                    class="mt-6 text-lg font-semibold leading-7 tracking-tight text-gray-900"
                  >
                    Forest Group
                  </h3>
                  <p
                    class="text-base font-semibold leading-6 text-slate-700 my-8"
                  >
                    Welcome to Forest Group: Your digital oasis for landscaped
                    parks. Explore lush green spaces, tranquil gardens, and
                    vibrant landscapes from the comfort of your screen. Discover
                    inspiration for your next outdoor adventure, family picnic,
                    or leisurely stroll.
                  </p>
                  <p class="w-full flex justify-around absolute bottom-0">
                    <span class="text-orange-600">HTML</span>
                    <span class="text-blue-600">CSS</span>
                    <span class="text-yellow-300">JavaScript</span>
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <script src="../scripts/modal.js"></script>
</Layout>
